  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Jeris Adventure Resort is on a full board basis. Your first meal will be dinner on arrival day and last meal will be breakfast on departure day.</p>
<p>Meals are often made with local and regional produce. Each morning you can enjoy a varied breakfast buffet with an assortment of hot and cold options. In the evening, you can enjoy a three-course meal often combing modern flavours with a Lappish twist. Plus one evening, you will have a special Christmas dinner. </p>
<p>Soft drinks and juice are included for children, a wristband will be provided on arrival. There is complimentary coffee and tea offered in the hotel's main restaurant throughout the opening hours.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
